45
</figureCitation>
; male genitalia as in 
<figureCitation box="[151,252,1902,1927]" captionStart="FIGURES 182 – 191" captionStartId="53.[151,264,1724,1747]" captionTargetBox="[168,1393,194,1683]" captionTargetId="figure@53.[160,1427,193,1703]" captionTargetPageId="53" captionText="FIGURES 182 – 191. Aedeagus images of Dima species. 182 — D. elateroides Charpentier, 1825, non-type specimen from Serbia; 183 — D. evritaniensis Schimmel &amp; Platia, 2008, non-type specimen from Timfristos Mts.; 184 — D. fialai sp. nov., holotype; 185 — D. florinensis Platia, 2012, non-type specimen; 186 — D. fthiotidensis Schimmel &amp; Platia, 2008, non-type specimen from Kallidromo Mts.; 187 — D. fthiotidensis, non-type specimen from Vardoussia Mts.; 188 — D. giachinoi Schimmel &amp; Platia 2008, non-type specimen; 189 — Dima sp. from Mani; 190 — D. hladilorum Schimmel, 1987, non-type specimen; 191 — D. kozufensis, sp. nov., holotype. Not to scale." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4670842" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4670842/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
